Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:37.39,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Um!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:39.91,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Did Sayaka-chan pass your test!?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:43.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’ve seen just how hard she’s worked for today’s performance!!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:50.35,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The whole time Kozue-senpai was out sick, she filled in for her! She even handled our practice schedules!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:10.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:44.93,Kaho,,0,0,0,,….O-Oh, come on…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:18.83,Kaho,,0,0,0,,This girl really is evil! Blegh!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.77,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You know what?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.23,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Hey, Sayaka.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.43,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:58.27,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Not only that, she also said she’d show you her answer in today’s performance, and you saw how amazing she just was!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:01.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You saw it, didn’t you!?\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:16.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,She’s doing that evil laugh again!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:14.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,G-Gah! You jerk!!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.72,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Battery died.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:06.01,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Hm. So you’re doing what you’re doing because you want to meet everyone’s expectations.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:09.87,Sachi,,0,0,0,,That’s why you’re a school idol, then.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.78,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…I’d say you conveyed that sentiment perfectly.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.40,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I see.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.04,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:06.78,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Pass, huh? Did she pass?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:09.82,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…hehe…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.38,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Na--hahahaha!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:20.98,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you even remember what the test was supposed to be for, Sayaka?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.22,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Finally get it?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:40.82,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Besides, from the moment you stood up to me back then, I already knew you’d found your answer.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:48.19,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, why not.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:52.49,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I ought to say it for posterity.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:57.10,Sachi,,0,0,0,, –Sayaka, you pass the third test!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:03.12,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Well isn’t that an unenthusiastic response.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.67,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, well!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:08.35,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Na–hahahaha!!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:22.52,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Sorry, sorry, did I take it too far?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:26.48,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Hm…?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.38,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Ahaha.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:34.07,Sachi,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was expecting you to react like Rurino and Kaho did.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:51.77,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Well, if you really did figure all that out, it’s because of your own efforts.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.73,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to do with it.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.77,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I’m not in the School Idol Club anymore, after all.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.82,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Heh, guess so.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:07.42,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Anyway… good luck.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.21,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Have fun with Love Live!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:25.97,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I fully got the message that you want to meet everyone’s expectations.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:32.30,Sachi,,0,0,0,,But why did you choose to convey that through a solo performance?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:04.63,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…You thought it would be easiest to understand if you were to have those expectations solely on you.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:06.63,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I see.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.63,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.99,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I honestly think it was amazing…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.09,Sachi,,0,0,0,,You really shone brightly up there.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.42,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Alright, you’ve been here long enough.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:22.46,Sachi,,0,0,0,,You can go back to Tsuzuri and the others now.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.54,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:56.03,Sachi,,0,0,0,,What a nice scene.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.03,Sachi,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:11.69,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:21.87,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think that the expectations people have of me are why I chose to become a school idol and why I want to be one.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:28.26,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,In that case…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:32.13,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,that’s all I have to say.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:03.12,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You two…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.41,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh? It was…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:27.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,for permission to use the stage… right?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:31.30,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Wait, that…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:59.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…A-Ah…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Sachi-senpai.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.30,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,No…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.76,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think I finally get what me…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.31,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,and the first-years as a whole need to improve on.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.94,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,All of this really helped me understand everything.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:01.18,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, you’re still our senior.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.63,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’ll try.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Alright, I’m gonna go now, Sachi-senpai.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.99,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That’s…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:43.30,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet everyone’s expectations.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I wanted to feel their weight.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:53.48,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I could feel myself becoming stronger through other people’s expectations…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:58.24,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And since I noticed that…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:09.98,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.60,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Alright.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.43,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Sachi-senpai.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:36.67,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Let’s go back, Rurino-san, Kaho-san…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.73,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:45.67,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Hmhm, let’s go.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
